702130f-a.title: Bronx: Westchester Avenue - Waters Avenue
702130f-a.text:
Westchester Ave. (left, where elevated structure is seen), east
side, north from Waters Ave. to Middletown Road, showing the swampy
meadow bounded on the right by Appleton Ave, and in the foreground by
Eaat Tremont Ave. (not seen). The elevated structure is that of the
I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway line.
July 9, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
